'''Monofilament line''', called '''''ohuludwu''''' in the [[Sy Bisti]] [[language]], was a type of thread. The [[Chiss]] [[Mitth'raw'nuruodo|Thrawn]] of the [[Chiss Ascendancy]] used monofilament line during the [[Imperial Era]] to catch a [[Alpha-3 Nimbus-class V-wing starfighter|V-wing starfighter]] and obtain the pilot's [[comlink]].<ref name="Thrawn">[[Thrawn (novel)|''Thrawn'']]</ref>

